{"tid":1008151,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"HH6338 入油唔撚排隊，過年仆街死","createTime":"2019-02-04T09:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T16:13:38.000Z","uid":72085,"like":165,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"76d0bf9a30d16e5215ff6639bf9338a5a6ca4ca4","tid":1008151,"uid":72085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:36:55.000Z","msg":"你老味，排勁耐隊你一野隊埋嚟，燈又唔打手又唔舉<br />\n條路岩岩好夠兩架車並行，成條龍都盡量駛左面留條路右面俾其他車行，你一個唔該後上左轉插入嚟，反應慢都撞隔離架26<br />\n仲要少少悔意都冇，幾十歲人頭髮都白晒少少禮貌都唔識，仲係度狡辯話唔知入油要排隊，頂你個肺，知道油站係邊，唔知條隊係邊？唔排隊入油唔通排隊去廁所？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果有巴打頭先第一城shell 入油搞慢左你地唔好意思，有D仆街唔屌唔撚鬆化，為禍人間<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yQTWrmC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyQTWrmC.png&h=2e7c41bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38c05cb6c8dbb94438c77a54d862a28ca8bfe7d1","tid":1008151,"uid":38047,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:39:18.000Z","msg":"通常做呢啲仆街嘢嘅都係啲中年大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671fba945fe53b14b96fc9f6965bcd1e93e54026","tid":1008151,"uid":73596,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:39:52.000Z","msg":"呢D真係要落車屌佢老母，幫佢全家開年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a33521e78379fe6f9474092cd1046ead5e4053","tid":1008151,"uid":12696,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"寶馬撚係咁上下"},{"pid":"ec8790b79acd7f2e33eedb42b31528c128968fd9","tid":1008151,"uid":72085,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"quote":{"pid":"f8a33521e78379fe6f9474092cd1046ead5e4053","tid":1008151,"uid":12696,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T09:54:24.000Z","msg":"寶馬撚係咁上下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T10:47:29.000Z","msg":"查實我都係寶馬撚，岩岩真係好撚慶，唔屌佢唔安樂，唔知要排隊但係又識打尖，死廢老"},{"pid":"51a81ee202ddadcc411accc19259df64312da625","tid":1008151,"uid":51171,"like":8,"dislike"